---
import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | CalcFalcon"
  description="Privacy policy for CalcFalcon calculator tools"
>
  <div class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="heading-lg mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none space-y-6">
        <p class="text-neutral-600">
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> March 2026
        </p>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            CalcFalcon is designed with privacy in mind. Our calculators run entirely in your browser -
            we do not collect, store, or transmit any personal information or calculation data to our servers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Calculator Data</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            All calculations are performed locally in your browser. When you use our calculators:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Your inputs and results are <strong>not</strong> sent to any server</li>
            <li>Calculator state may be encoded in the URL for sharing purposes - this is entirely optional</li>
            <li>We do not track individual calculation sessions</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Email Communications</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            If you subscribe to our newsletter, we collect your email address to send you tax tips, calculator updates, and related content. Your email is stored with our email service provider, <a href="https://resend.com/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Resend</a>.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>We only collect your email address - no other personal data</li>
            <li>You can unsubscribe at any time via the link in every email</li>
            <li>We never sell or share your email address with third parties</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            We use minimal cookies and tracking:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> May be used for basic site functionality</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> We may use privacy-focused analytics to understand site usage in aggregate</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Advertising</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            We display advertisements through Google AdSense to support the free tools on this site. When ads are shown:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to this site or other websites</li>
            <li>Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on your browsing history</li>
            <li>You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Google Ads Settings</a></li>
            <li>You can opt out of third-party vendor cookies at <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">aboutads.info</a></li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            For more information on how Google uses data, see <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Affiliate Links</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Some pages on CalcFalcon contain affiliate links to products and services we recommend. When you click an affiliate link and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. These recommendations are based on genuine evaluation and relevance to our calculator tools. Affiliate partnerships do not influence our calculator results or editorial content.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our site may include:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li><strong>Google AdSense:</strong> Displays advertisements. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Resend:</strong> Email newsletter delivery. <a href="https://resend.com/legal/privacy-policy" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Resend Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Hosting:</strong> Our site is hosted on Railway. <a href="https://railway.app/legal/privacy" class="text-primary-600 hover:underline">Railway Privacy Policy</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            You have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-neutral-600 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>Use our calculators without creating an account</li>
            <li>Clear your browser data at any time</li>
            <li>Opt out of personalized advertising through your browser settings</li>
            <li>Unsubscribe from email communications at any time</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your email from our mailing list</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through our website.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-600 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page
            with an updated revision date.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
